annotations.description: Learn how the make the Little Wing, a delicious bourbon cocktail recipe. I actually like this Paper Plane riff better then the original. #bourbon #cocktail #...
annotations.title: DELICIOUS BOURBON COCKTAIL RECIPE, The Little Wing - A Paper Plane riff

textContent:
1 oz Bourbon
1 oz Aperol
1 oz St-Germain
1 oz Fresh lemon juice
2 Slices of cucumber

Pour all ingredients including cucumber in a cocktail shaker filled with ice.
Shake for about 10 seconds
Fine strain in a chilled cocktail coupe
Garnish with a slice of cucumber
